Maintainer: The package maintainer <martina.paganin95@gmail.com>
Description: expressyouRcell is a unique and easy-to-use R package which provides an 
    intuitive approach for visualizing and presenting multi-dimensional variations of 
    gene expression levels across time and space. This tool gives the possibility of 
    generating animations of pictographic representations of cells, or pictograms, 
    providing a convenient and intuitive method for visualizing and understanding time course variations 
    in cellular compartments. A range of customizable options is 
    provided to create cellular pictograms starting from your data! :)
